OL,3,CCornish couple finally find home after
OL,4,Cthree years living in friend's garden
OL,6,FA Cornish couple have finally found a
OL,7,Fhome after living in a caravan for
OL,8,Fthree and half years due to the
OL,9,Fcounty's housing crisis.
OL,11,FSupport workers Emma and Mike Beason
OL,12,Fmoved into a caravan in their friend's
OL,13,Fgarden after their landlord told them
OL,14,Fthey needed their old home back.
OL,16,FNow living in a brand new one-bedroom
OL,17,Fflat, they can't believe their luck.
