OL,6,F"Essentially, if you want to have a
OL,7,Froof over your head, you have to do
OL,8,Fabout three jobs or work like 50 hours
OL,9,Fa week and scrimp and save and just
OL,10,Fkind of spend your entire life doing
OL,11,Fthat. And I think that makes me feel
OL,12,Ffrustrated."
