OL,4,Cthree years living in friend's garden
OL,6,FHomes for Cornwall is a group trying
OL,7,Fto come up with practical solutions to
OL,8,Ffix the current "broken" housing
OL,9,Fsystem.
OL,11,FEmma Stratton, CEO of the Scarlett and
OL,12,FBedruthan Hotels, said we need to
OL,13,Fchallenge the norm.
OL,15,FShe said: "We recognise that it's
OL,16,Freally complex. The system is broken.
OL,18,F"So there's lots of things we've been
OL,19,Ftalking to, lots of planners about how
OL,20,Ffar can be, how far can we push the
OL,21,Fthe planning system.
