OL,6,F"And we've actually come up with
OL,7,Fsomething called our Acre project,
OL,8,Fwhich we are looking at, where
OL,9,Fcommunities can acquire land for the
OL,10,Fhousing that they want and stay, you
OL,11,Fknow, have a really big say in the
OL,12,Fsort of housing that is built and also
OL,13,Fstay in control in it.
OL,15,F"They could own it in perpetuity for
OL,16,Fhouses forever and have those houses
OL,17,Fbeing given to local workers, which
OL,18,Ffeels really exciting."
