OL,6,FThe Acre Project is one way architects
OL,7,Fand housing professionals could donate
OL,8,Ftheir skills, giving parish councils a
OL,9,Fshortcut to making small developments
OL,10,Fa reality.
OL,12,FSam Galsworthy, the owner of the
OL,13,FTrewithen estate, is in a position to
OL,14,Fdonate land but said philanthropy is a
OL,15,Fsmall part of Homes for Cornwall's
OL,16,Fideas for changing attitudes to the
OL,17,Fcounty's housing problems.
