OL,6,FHe said: "There's a great fear within
OL,7,Fthe Duchy that we just need to
OL,8,Fconcrete over this extraordinarily
OL,9,Fspecial county of ours and that's not
OL,10,Fthe case at all.
OL,12,F"I mean, actually the county needs 50
OL,13,Fto 60,000 homes by 2030. 0.8% of the
OL,14,Flandmass of housing.
OL,16,F"I hope that we can find the right
OL,17,Fbalance providing the right kind of
OL,18,Fhousing."
